description: Online Brands Nordic AB engages in the provision of online retail. The firm operates online shops with jewelry made primarily of gold and silver, namely hedbergsguld.se and jewel.se, as well as operates a shop in Dalsjofors, Sweden. The firm operates such subsidiaries as Hedbergs Guld & Silver AB, Juvelerare Eric G Andersson AB, Juvelerare John Victorin i Varberg AB and Ideguld AB.
naics: Jewelry, Luggage, and Leather Goods Stores
name: Online Brands Nordic AB
